  <brief_title>Vildagliptin in Older Adults With Diabetes and Mild Cognitive Impairment</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Vildagliptin, a DPP-4 Inhibitor, in Elderly Diabetic Patients With Mild Cognitive Impairment</official_title>
